listings.name: 2 bedroom apartment of 60 m² in Amsterdam
listings.detailsDescription: Completely newly renovated three-room apartment (2 bedrooms), with terrace of 10m2.The beautiful house is located in a fully renovated monumental canal house from 1906, at the Nieuwe Prinsengracht.The apartment is located in the popular Plantage area of ??the Central district.It is conveniently located in relation to the Utrechtsestraat and Rembrandt Square. In close proximity include the Botanical Gardens, the Hermitage, Artis Zoo, Stopera and Royal Theatre Carré.For daily shopping you will find several supermarkets within walking distance (Roetersstraat, Sarphatistraat, Nieuwe Kerkstraat).The property is easily accessible by both car and public transport. Within walking distance are several tram and metro stops.layout

listings.location: 68 Rue de Flores du Blumen, Paris 75007,  France

listings.name: Contemporary Modern House Design
listings.detailsDescription: Located in Khamis Mushait, Saudi Arabia, this Contemporary Modern House Design by CAS is a brilliant way to evoke a resort-like luxurious vibe in your own home. Extremely simple & modernistic, the artful design of this home perfectly encompasses the cultural & traditional settings of the site context. The wood-glass combo against a backdrop of white makes a bold statement while the gorgeous orthogonally oriented landscape helps emulate the best of nature within the bounds of the property itself.
